<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8"/>
        <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Grotesk:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
        <style>
            h1 { font-size: 40px; font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif; }
            h2 { font-size: 30px; }
            p  { font-size: 14px; }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        <p>Hi,</p>
        <p>
            We came across your website <strong>${domain}</strong> and we think it would be
            a great fit for our Blogger Outreach platform, <strong>Slinky Linky</strong>.
        </p>
        <p>
            We connect content marketers and PR agencies with quality website owners like yourself.
            As a supplier on our platform, you would receive paid article placement requests directly
            via email for a pre agreed fee. For your website we would suggest a price of ${currencySymbol}${suggestedFee} per article
            which will include up to 3 links, but you can amend this when you join. No cold outreach,
            no chasing. If the content sent doesn't suit your website, simply decline and you can
            review the next paid placement.
        </p>
        <p>
            If you're interested, please click <a href="${responseUrl}">here</a> to find
            out more and register your interest. You can also upload a list of other sites
            you manage, or share a link to a Google Doc with your site portfolio.
        </p>
        <p>
            If you'd rather not hear from us again, you can decline on the same page and
            we'll remove you from our list.
        </p>
        <p>Any questions, feel free to get in touch.</p>
        <p>Regards,</p>
        <p>
            <em>${signoff}</em><br/>
            <em>${signoffContactDetails}</em>
        </p>
        <img src="cid:logo-cid" width="53px" style="float:left"/>
        <h1 style="float:left; margin-left:10px; margin-top:0px;"><span style="color: #333;">Slinky</span><span style="color: #a89dbd;">Linky</span></h1>
    </body>
</html>
